race.comment: TOO DARN SASSY (9) spiked his figures when beaten narrowly this track/distance. He's hinted of better things to come here three back and off a brief freshen is well placed to go one better. DIAMOND FROST (7) resumed at Wagga and went close. He maps well and has more to give. McDougall sticks aboard and that's a decent push for his chances. ALABAMA HUSSY (6) positions forward and won her Maiden comfortably at Wagga as expected. Should have more to give and maps for the run of the race. DEEPWATER ARTIST (2) can progress off the good fresh effort and go close.
